## The Three Difficulty Levels

| Task | What Changes | Why It's Harder |
|------|-------------|-----------------|
| **task_easy** | Clean consumer, 16 flat fields, identity pre-verified | Agent just classifies by field name semantics |
| **task_medium** | Different email than account, support ticket transcripts | Must verify identity proportionally, redact at sentence level |
| **task_hard** | Employee Slack export, threaded messages, aliased user IDs | Must resolve aliases, split mixed-ownership sentences, handle Article 9 escalation |

Currently only `task_easy` is fully implemented. Tasks 2 & 3 use the same generator temporarily (they'll produce different, harder data once implemented).

