## Summary

This environment turns a **$1,500 manual compliance task** into a **structured RL training problem**. An untrained LLM scores 0.65-0.75. With RL post-training (PPO/GRPO running thousands of episodes against the reward function), an agent can learn to score **0.90+** by:

1. Always querying both silos first
2. Correctly identifying personal data fields by semantic understanding
3. Never leaking internal analytical metrics
4. Operating efficiently within the step budget

The environment is fully deterministic, reproducible, containerized, and compatible with all major RL training frameworks.
